<h2>Anything else?</h2>
<p>
  Well, if you insist, here are a few rules, just in case your good judgement has gone on vacation:
</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Be polite and respectful.</strong> Other players might add you to their ban lists if you offend them, and then you will not have any friends, and that will make you sad. Know your audience; if you're not sure if the other other players in the game would appreicate a drawing of a penis, ask in chat.
  <li><strong>Don't break the law.</strong> Things that are illegal in real life are also illegal on the internet. Don't use material you don't own. (Remixing, referencing, satirizing, recontextualizing, and other exceptions for fair use obviously apply.) Don't share images that might cause the FBI to knock on your door one day. Maybe just delete those images from your hard drive, while you're at it. Please don't use this service to discuss terrorist plots or anything; the chat is permenantly logged and I really don't want to get subpoenaed. Thanks!
  <li>And again, <strong>HAVE FUN!</strong> If you break this rule, the FBI will find you for sure.
</ul>